query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('apple',
'codereview',
'dba',
'drupal',
'salesforce')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('8',
'algorithm',
'applications',
'c++11',
'database',
'datetime',
'finder',
'itunes',
'javascript',
'mountain-lion',
'yosemite')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
